{"tid":21061,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［遊記］毒遊台灣一個禮拜 有問盡答","createTime":"2016-12-03T15:50:21.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T16:49:22.000Z","uid":15878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c3131027d8c6daeeab5fde4e7e25f89fd3e5bd27","tid":21061,"uid":15878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:50:21.000Z","msg":"一直都冇諗過自己有一日竟然夠膽一個人戇鳩鳩去旅行 所以出post 紀錄下第一次出城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己係一個好hea既人所以行程其實唔可以比大家用黎參考 可能一日就係hea下hea下咁<br />\n<br />\n利申 我而家仲人在台北 day4 所以未必可以日日出post"},{"pid":"50977137a280baec19a6d0d20ae882f9035f6dfa","tid":21061,"uid":28019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:55:03.000Z","msg":"去食一燈拉麵"},{"pid":"6c9aa48ea2250279010d8db140583b5c452c30dd","tid":21061,"uid":28019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:56:56.000Z","msg":"搵日平日去淡水河邊hea，放空，睇下日落，望下身邊既人同事"},{"pid":"06984e4052ec547a61af57e42fb17b049a26814b","tid":21061,"uid":15878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:07:44.000Z","msg":"講番DAY 1 先<br />\n係香港1020機坐華航去高雄 好成功咁早一個半鐘到機場 寄埋行李入得閘出埋境諗住可以BORADING準備上機食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  點知遇到DELAY 睇住格離架都係華航但飛台北走埋都未到我班機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n影相係紀錄 自己影相好屎 唔好介意<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/a/fPmg2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fa%2FfPmg2&h=8058532e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後尾其實唔係等左好耐 大概1130就起飛 係自己戇鳩冇食野出門口所以覺得耐 講番機程 其實台妹空姐真係幾多靚女但唔敢偷拍人 無相勿屌 佢地仲好好人 我問佢地拎汽水 我國語好爛 發極都發唔岩音 佢地好有耐性聽我講同問清楚我 不過機程太快 大概1230就降落左係高雄機場"},{"pid":"141fa11bdf3073bc7086ce91ca8cd674dbe267e0","tid":21061,"uid":15878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:07:55.000Z","msg":"講番DAY 1 先<br />\n係香港1020機坐華航去高雄 好成功咁早一個半鐘到機場 寄埋行李入得閘出埋境諗住可以BORADING準備上機食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  點知遇到DELAY 睇住格離架都係華航但飛台北走埋都未到我班機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n影相係紀錄 自己影相好屎 唔好介意<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/a/fPmg2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fa%2FfPmg2&h=8058532e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後尾其實唔係等左好耐 大概1130就起飛 係自己戇鳩冇食野出門口所以覺得耐 講番機程 其實台妹空姐真係幾多靚女但唔敢偷拍人 無相勿屌 佢地仲好好人 我問佢地拎汽水 我國語好爛 發極都發唔岩音 佢地好有耐性聽我講同問清楚我 不過機程太快 大概1230就降落左係高雄機場"},{"pid":"3864db33875b61c54c439c91bdee165b9745f774","tid":21061,"uid":15878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:08:59.000Z","msg":"Lihkg太快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 回左post都唔知禁多左次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e7b347003f98d85d425aa28c8300622eee1b3c1","tid":21061,"uid":6166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:09:44.000Z","msg":"死圖"},{"pid":"9a183d5e6f7930447d34f2a96c113cfc414e5178","tid":21061,"uid":15878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:10:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵日平日去淡水河邊hea，放空，睇下日落，望下身邊既人同事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我而家台北就住係朋友淡水屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6a606aec2f4aa257ff607bc06b12d15a83163d","tid":21061,"uid":35698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:11:10.000Z","msg":"高雄有咩玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"7aacbc1b66d8ab1f5fd22df16f9209e0141f8a04","tid":21061,"uid":15878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:13:00.000Z","msg":"原來死左圖 係web版打字用imgur up 有冇其他up圖網介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n定轉用app up<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/04/001220_b58bd510cd02b688763f25ec27c19345.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F04%2F001220_b58bd510cd02b688763f25ec27c19345.jpg&h=9e9e1410&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影相技術好劣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係純紀錄"},{"pid":"64c23a0640b96ecf8883ae2fb6f205ef96a0ed84","tid":21061,"uid":15878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:18:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高雄有咩玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔係去左好多地方 留左3日2夜 第3日仲要冇去地方淨係去左高鐵站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我建議可以去太魯閣玩卡丁車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己有野買所以揀左去夢時代就冇去到太魯閣商場 <br />\n<br />\n鐘意影相可以去85大樓但唔建議上去喇要收門票 可以去搭輕軌到高雄展覽館附近都影到成座大樓<br />\n<br />\n仲有可以去睇西子灣日落同去旗津食海鮮睇燈塔望海"},{"pid":"a14e46327f610ff63090109ddc62c85c1bbaa443","tid":21061,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:27:09.000Z","msg":"劉鳴先"},{"pid":"ed94aa6e34116fd04ffcd12aae15f00d73afe18e","tid":21061,"uid":15878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:39:18.000Z","msg":"Day1續<br />\n<br />\n留意番高雄係冇悠遊卡賣得一張一卡通ipass賣 呢張卡都可以係台北用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n買左所有野就出發去hostel放低行李出去玩<br />\n係axxxa book既 係新hostel 亦都好近捷運站 捷運站出口就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好方便後門出去就係六合夜市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/04/003727_5fc4154bf6ac0fa09dc382bf53cd6231.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F04%2F003727_5fc4154bf6ac0fa09dc382bf53cd6231.jpg&h=653c2828&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n房仲有其他人所以簡單snapshot 一張 間房其實唔錯只有一個問題 就係新裝修完既木味仲未散得哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw台灣最美既風景係人係堅既<br />\nHostel既小管家見出面有雨所以好好人咁比我提早checkin左 又有話定比我聽邊個夜市今日唔會開 就係hostel執下行李休息左個幾鐘先再出去繼續行程"},{"pid":"0b613afb3aca317dc02b0862bda5cc01e7f9b664","tid":21061,"uid":45508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:42:13.000Z","msg":"成個trip用左幾錢"},{"pid":"1a3f5a26aa4c00ddee325f65fa2e833295c0362f","tid":21061,"uid":15878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:43:57.000Z","msg":"聽日再繼續打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽日會HEA一日<br />\n只會去附近淡水老街買下野睇下日落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"781c06675dcd19faf76ec3a614c4849ba2e7a812","tid":21061,"uid":15878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:49:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成個trip用左幾錢</blockquote><br />\n暫時黎講 計埋機票住宿禁左出黎既錢係4500左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過樓主我係岩岩變左做失業廢青 有咁慳就盡慳咁去<br />\n機票係淨係比稅 中左個活動既獎之後當比個機會自己重新整理下而家生活"}]}